data.description: Seller is offering $15,000 in concessions for buyer to assist with closing costs, rate buy down, or roof replacement!!    Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom retreat offering a multitude of luxurious amenities and endless potential. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this home presents an exceptional blend of comfort and style. Delight in the elegance of the kitchen with its gleaming quartz countertops and meticulously crafted solid wood cabinets, providing both functionality and beauty. There is a second living space that can be used as a Den/4th bedroom/Playroom/Office or Hobby room. The master bathroom is a sanctuary of tranquility, featuring exquisite quartz countertops, a new vanity, and a tastefully appointed design. The guest bathroom has been thoughtfully renovated with a new vanity, toilet, sink, and flooring, ensuring both style and convenience. Revel in the allure of brand-new, waterproof, scratch-resistant vinyl plank flooring that is in all floors except bedrooms, which have all new plush carpeting. Backyard has all vinyl privacy fencing, a newer deck with new spa and a lighted gazebo area. Detached Garage/Workshop (with 220 amp installed). Mature landscaping and interior exterior of home have recently been painted. This home will not last! Come check out all it has to offer before its gone!
